    <h2 id="communication-principles-bad1785b" class="heading heading--two heading--sf">Communication principles</h2>



    <div class="rich-text"><p data-block-key="aj0pi">The strategic report and the annual report are communication between companies and their shareholders. We encourage companies to use the following communication principles to enhance the quality of their corporate reporting.</p><p data-block-key="f6ig2"><a href="/documents/9099/FRC_Communication_Principles.pdf">Communication Principles infographic (February 2026)</a></p></div>

    
    <h2 id="clarifications-of-the-regulations-a9e6fca7" class="heading heading--two heading--sf">Clarifications of the Regulations</h2>



    <div class="rich-text"><ol><li data-block-key="e68f4">While developing the initial 2014 Guidance, the FRC worked closely with the Department for Business, Innovation and Skills (BIS), now the Department for Business and Trade (DBT). During the consultation process the FRC received a number of queries on legal matters related to the 2013 Regulations. BIS provided clarifications on these matters in a <a href="/documents/4174/BIS_letter_guidance_on_narrative_reporting.pdf">letter to the FRC</a> (PDF).</li><li data-block-key="bqpmp">In respect of 'The Companies (Miscellaneous Reporting) Regulations 2018', the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (BEIS), now DBT, issued some <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/corporate-governance-new-reporting-regulations">frequently asked questions</a> to support the legislative requirements. Guidance on the application of the section 172 duty is provided by the GC100 and the Investor Group.</li><li data-block-key="2pf14"><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/climate-related-financial-disclosures-for-companies-and-limited-liability-partnerships-llps">Guidance in the form of non-binding Q&amp;A</a> to support companies and LLPs in their application of the climate-related financial requirements was prepared by BEIS, now the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero (DESNZ).</li></ol></div>

    
    <h2 id="further-information-including-previous-editions-03959434" class="heading heading--two heading--sf">Further information including previous editions</h2>



    

<div class="file-list importance-secondary">
    <table class="govuk-table">
        <caption id="files-list-documents">
            <div class="file-list__heading">
                Documents
            </div>
            
        </caption>

        <tbody class="govuk-table__body file-list__table">
            
                <tr class="govuk-table__row file-list__table-row">
